# Assuming you have a PES or good guess of TS geometry (here continued from PES HCO3- reaction example). 
# Take the PES highest energy point or your own guess geoemtry prepared as 'opt_step10.xyz' and run optTS. 
# If very sure, use 'FREQ' keyword to obtain one imaginary mode. 
!r2SCAN-3c OptTS

*xyzfile 0 1 opt_step10.xyz
